[div class=p 
	"Encoding notes:
	$LF
	"Native aspect ratio is roughly 4:3, letterboxed to roughly 16:9.  Please crop out the letterboxing if encoded.
	$LF
	"Dumping frames and audio from the start causes audio to be longer than video.  Starting dump of both at the initial Loading text window causes them to match.
	$LF
	"Dolphin dumps 59.94 hz video, apparently duplicating each frame.  In VirtualDub I processed every other frame in my high res texture encode for 29.97 hz to save file size with no loss of quality.
	$LF
	"I recommend TASVideos encode use default textures, this would be consistent with all my other RE4 Mercenaries publications and would differentiate it from my encode with high res textures on Youtube.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"If published to Youtube, please include link to my HD Project encode at the bottom of the description, similar to this:  "Ubercapitalist has provided an encode of the movie with HD Project textures: 
	[a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZD4G5KaBQ0 rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZD4G5KaBQ0
	]a
	""
